om the comparison\nalso suggest the development of collaborative intelligence that keeps\nhuman-in-the-loop of AI models to further enhance the reliability of AI-enabled\nsafety functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Aug 2021 16:08:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Nov 2022 21:23:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-11"}
