 0.10\\ {\\rm yr}^{-1}$ for LIGO at\ndesign sensitivity and $(0.6 - 2.4) \\times 10^3\\ {\\rm yr}^{-1}$ for the future\nthird generation ground-based detector Cosmic Explorer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Aug 2021 22:15:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 Jan 2022 00:05:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-14"}
