all graphs in $\\mathcal{F}_n$ are DGS as\n$n\\rightarrow \\infty$. This gives a supporting evidence for Haemers' conjecture\nthat almost all graphs are determined by their spectra.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Aug 2021 07:33:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2021 08:24:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-10"}
