es. We\nalso show that grains from the impacting dune spread with a diffusion-like\ncomponent over the target barchan, and we propose a diffusion length. Our\nresults provide new insights into the size-regulating mechanisms of barchans\nand barchanoid forms found on Earth and other planets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Aug 2021 13:47:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-24"}
